name: The Fluf With No Name
description: The prairie wind burned hot across his face. Remnants of his carrot ranch and burrow seared away in the blistering inferno. His brow furrowed and the hairs on his chin and ears singed in the heat. That fateful day he could not turn his eyes away, for the fire that took everything he built was locked in them forever. It's been months since anyone in the burrows last saw him. What was his name again? Nobody knew but his friends call him 'Joe'. He was last seen carving on a piece of charred wood "I will take back what's mine. I'll be back!".

He is the premier fur stylist to the Fluf stars, and is best known as the artist who perfected the Tuft and the Mohawk. Sir John worked with McRabbit for a year and then as an assistant to Carrot Toppler, who became their mentor. Their gifts were swiftly acknowledged, and they rapidly gained an impressive client list.

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: Sometimes Clarence asks me what I would have done if he had died, if that bullet had been two inches more to the left. To this I always smile as if I'm not going to satisfy him with a response. But I always do. I tell him of how I would want to die, but that the anguish and the want of death would fade like the stars at dawn, and that things would be much as they are now. Perhaps.
